            <h4 class="fontWeight500">Before:</h4>
            <h4> Packages were <span class="fontWeight400">only visible inside provider shops</span>, functioning as <span class="fontWeight400">late-stage upsells</span>.</h4>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="Grid-cell">
          <div class="element">
            <img class="modal-target card2026" src="discover_after.png" alt="Packages surfaced before provider selection">
            <h4 class="fontWeight500">After:</h4>

            <h4> Standardized packages surfaced during browsing, <span class="fontWeight400">enabling discovery before provider selection. </span></h4>

          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="Grid-cell">
          <div class="element">
            <img class="modal-target card2026" src="discover_future.png" alt="Packages mapped into categories when fulfillment can be validated">
            <h4 class="fontWeight500">Future</h4>

            <h4>Integrate packages into categories once supply coverage and availability validation <span class="fontWeight400">support reliable fulfillment.</span> </h4>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="spacingMedium"></div>

    <div class="spacingXLarge"></div>

    <div class="spacingLarge"></div>


    <div class="spacingMedium"></div>





  </section>

